        "text_PJxJEe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>On Love<\/h3><p>You will see sensual, nurturing love. The emotional safety this offers will extend intimacy to new depths. Offer yourself plainly, wholly. <\/p><h3>On Health<\/h3><p>You must take the time to focus on resting and on your nourishment. If you don’t take a breath, you will only hurt yourself. <\/p><h3>On Money \/ Career<\/h3><p>Creative projects will likely flourish. Be patient, don’t put pressure on yourself, and take it slower. You are doing well enough as you are. <br\/><br\/><br\/>How to work with this energy <\/p><h3>Slow down, and take help as and when you need it. <\/h3><h3>Recommended products<\/h3><ol><li>Sunday Rituals Hair Repair & Growth Oil – Steady growth<br\/><\/li><li>Rose Apple Bag Charm (Apple) – Abundance <br\/><\/li><li>Artisanal Beaded Bag – Life in Bloom Edition – Nourishment<br\/><\/li><li>Enamel pin (Forget me not) – Reminders of love<\/li><\/ol><p><br\/>You can find these in our pop-up booth at Night At Orchard, along the outdoor pathway between Ngee Ann City & Ion Orchard between 26-28 Dec, 3pm onwards <\/p>",
            "text_size": "typeset2",
            "secondary_color": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
